
<button type="button" href="/sales" class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-transparent text-sm font-medium rounded-full shadow-sm text-white bg-emerald-300 hover:bg-emerald-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-indigo-500"><a href="/sales">Go back</a></button>





